    <item>
      <title>荷兰机构称，诺和诺德的 Wegovy 成本过高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/novo-nordisk-s-wegovy-will-cost-too-much-dutch-agency-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰卫生保健机构警告称，荷兰不应承担诺和诺德公司 Wegovy 的费用，因为该药物价格过于昂贵，且该减肥药的长期效益存在“重大不确定性”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/novo-nordisk-s-wegovy-will-cost-too-much-dutch-agency-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:50:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
